query: SELECT s.id, s.coachId, cp.slug FROM sessions s JOIN coach_profiles cp ON s.coachId = cp.id WHERE cp.slug IN ('soukaina-mhammedi-alaoui', 'preciosa-baganha', 'victor-amisi', 'francine-nkurunziza') AND s.status = 'completed' LIMIT 10
